name: Jax Norveel
content: Jax Norveel was a male Human smuggler who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. During the Clone Wars, he served as a lieutenant to Zelice Sturm, a fallen Jedi who lead a smuggling gang that was based on the planet Genarius. He was present in the Dark Edge Dancetorium, a building that was used by Sturm as a hideout, when the Heroes of Cularin traveled there to confront the former Jedi.
